
Sentiment Analysis of IMDB Movie reviews

A basic Naive Bayes classifier using many NLP preprocessing techniques is implemented.

The training set details

 2500 positive reviews
2500 negative reviews

Test set used:
 2500 positive reviews
 2500 negative reviews

Currently only Bag of Words features are used which gives a pretty decent accuracy of 81.2 %.

Additional Features will be added soon

1) POS Tag based features
2) TF_IDF features
3) Sentiment Lexicon polarity scores
4) Co-occurence Features

Usage:
Run python classify_sentiment.py

Requirements: 

1) NLTK -

sudo easy_install nltk

2) Use NLTK downloader to get the corpora needed in the code 

ipython
import nltk
nltk.download()

